Cell["\<\
Having already evaluated this derivative above, we can readily observe that \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.92132983622705*^9, 
  3.9213298519408555`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"404ea9b9-9450-4c93-83c7-\
