    3.921329587709283*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "45d1e7b7-09f0-40b0-9b6f-2e1893033d78"],
 " is an energy of translation of an individual particle, we can relate the \
average translational energy ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{"\[LeftAngleBracket]", 
   SubscriptBox["\[CurlyEpsilon]", 
    StyleBox["trans",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}]],
